cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.CC, cs.DM, cs.CG. 

The paper deals with communication complexity and lower bounds for data stream algorithms. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.IT (Information Theory) are the most likely categories as they directly relate to the main topic of the paper. cs.CC (Computational Complexity) and cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) are also likely categories as they are closely related to communication complexity. Finally, cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a less likely category, but it is mentioned in the paper as an example of a problem that can be reduced to the communication complexity problem studied in the paper.
